# Bota Driver Python bindings

Python binding for the Bota Driver C++ library.

For more information about the Bota Driver Python API, please refer to the [Bota Driver documentation](https://code.botasys.com/en/gen_a/layer1/driver/driver_py.html).

For an usage example, please refer to the following repository: [bota_driver_py_example](https://gitlab.com/botasys/drivers/bota_driver_py_example).

For a general start guideline with Bota Systems Force Torque sensors, please refer to the [Bota Systems startpage](https://shop.botasys.com/start).